<!--    Public document type definition. Typical invocation:
<!DOCTYPE art PUBLIC "-//BMC//DTD FULL LENGTH ARTICLE//EN" []>
-->
<!--


	History:
	Version 0.41
					add new optional 'trans-abs-grp' tag to 'fm' for marking-up translated abstracts
